Class NotificationFood

  • java.lang.Object
    • Food.NotificationFood

  • public class NotificationFood
extends java.lang.Object
    the class Food.NotificationFood is used to create a new notification for a certain food
    in which the class Food.Food is called to associate each notification with a certain food
